high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the left end of the counter.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Look down to face the edge of the counter.
Place the apple on the edge of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the back of the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Place the knife on the counter beside the apple.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to face the right side of the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and turn to the right to face the trash can.
Place the piece of apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To clean a piece of apple and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Go to the counter beside the stove
Pick up the apple on the counter
Look up while holding the apple
Put the apple back down on the table
Pick up the knife on the counter
Cut the apple with the knife
Put the knife back down on the counter
Pick up the cut apple piece
Go to the sink
Wash the apple in the sink
Walk to the bin
Put the apple piece in the bin
anns.task_desc: Cut, wash, and throw away an apple piece

high_descs: Turn left and head to the small counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the apple in front of the tomato.
Lift the apple up towards the counter.
Put the apple on the edge of the counter.
Pick up the knife from under the tomato.
Cut the apple with the knife.
Put the knife on the counter to the left of the apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter.
Turn right and head to the sink.
Put the slice of apple in the sink, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn left, go pass the end of the counter and turn right towards the trash can.
Put the slice of apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of apple in the trash can.
